\p 
\v 24 \w David|strong="H1732"\w* talked gently \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* wife, \w Bathsheba|strong="H1339"\w*, \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w make|strong="H7901"\w* \w her|strong="H7121"\w* feel \w better|strong="H5162"\w*. \w And|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w slept|strong="H7901"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w her|strong="H7121"\w*, \w as|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H1121"\w* \w sleeps|strong="H7901"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* wife. \w And|strong="H1121"\w* \w she|strong="H7121"\w* \w had|strong="H3068"\w* another \w baby|strong="H1121"\w* boy, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* \w named|strong="H7121"\w* \w him|strong="H3205"\w* \em Solomon\em*. \w God|strong="H3068"\w* loved \w that|strong="H3068"\w* little boy very much.
